{/* Hero Section */}

Pass CELPIP & Get Your Canadian PR with Confidence

Join our CELPIP Speaking Club and practice with other immigrants like you. TESOL-certified instructor • Proven CLB improvement • Small groups • Supportive community

25-minute trial • See if we're a good fit FREE
🎓 TESOL Certified
📜 Cambridge Business English
🎯 CELPIP Instructor

Masha

English Teacher & CELPIP Specialist

⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ 3+ Years Experience
{/* About Section */}

Why Work With Me?

I specialize in working with adult learners who want to take their English to the next level. Most of my students already know some English but lack structure, confidence, or a clear path forward.

💡

Clear Explanations

I explain things clearly and help you understand not just what to study, but why and how to apply it in real life.

🎯

Focused Feedback

Get targeted feedback that addresses your specific areas for improvement with concrete action steps.

📈

Progress Tracking

Track your progress with structured lessons and clear milestones to keep you motivated.

🌍

Multilingual Support

Lessons are in English, but I also speak Russian and Ukrainian to help when you need it most.

Professional Credentials

🇨🇦

TESOL Diploma

Canada - Teaching English to Speakers of Other Languages

🎯

CELPIP Instructor Certificate

Certified to prepare students for Canadian immigration English tests

🏢

Cambridge Business English Certificate

Specialized training in professional English communication

{/* Testimonials Section */}

What My Students Say

Real feedback from students I've helped

"We've had about ten lessons so far, and my main goal is to prepare for the CELPIP English test. Masha has created an excellent study plan and helps me with my weak areas. She is always punctual, and I'm happy to continue learning with her. Her approach is organized and focused, which gives me confidence as I get closer to my test date."

Mariia

CELPIP Student
⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐

"Masha is a great teacher, since I started learning with her I have seen my level of English improve, all the classes are very productive and practical. She is kind, patient and always in a great mood. Highly recommended!"

Viktoriia

English Student
⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐

"Masha is a very professional tutor. While we are making conversations, she is also checking my English, immediately points out to me about my mistakes. She really cares about my progress in English and building my confidence in communication."

Ivanna

English Student
⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
🌟 5.0/5 stars • 7 reviews on Preply
{/* Trial Lesson Section */}

Try Before You Join Our Speaking Club

25-minute trial lesson to see if our CELPIP Speaking Club is right for you

1

Assessment & Goals

I ask questions to understand your current level, goals, and motivation

2

Quick Task

You do a short task so I can see how you use English right now

3

Feedback & Plan

I give brief feedback and explain which formats might be a good fit

You'll leave with: A clear idea of your CELPIP level, specific areas to improve, and an invitation to join our Speaking Club if it's a good fit.

Book Your Trial Now

$25 CAD FREE

Limited time offer while I'm building my schedule

✅ No commitment required
{/* Services Section */}

Choose Your CELPIP Journey

Three simple paths to CELPIP success - start with a free trial

CELPIP Speaking Club

Small Groups Most Popular

Practice CELPIP speaking with other immigrants in a supportive group environment. Perfect for building confidence and improving your CLB level.

  • Weekly group speaking practice
  • All CELPIP speaking task types
  • Peer support from other immigrants
  • Affordable group rates
  • Progress tracking and feedback

Free Trial Lesson

25 Minutes

Test drive our teaching style and get personalized CELPIP feedback before committing to anything.

  • CELPIP level assessment
  • Personalized feedback
  • Speaking Club recommendation
  • No commitment required
  • 100% FREE

1-on-1 CELPIP Intensive

Private

Accelerated CELPIP preparation with personalized attention for urgent deadlines or specific needs.

  • All 4 CELPIP skills
  • Customized study plan
  • Flexible scheduling
  • Intensive feedback
  • Premium support
{/* Pricing Section */}

Flexible Pricing for Every Goal

Pricing depends on your goals and the format you choose. After the trial, I'll suggest a plan that fits your needs.

Investment Range

CAD $15 - $55 per session

Pricing depends on:

  • Lesson format (1-on-1 vs group)
  • Session duration
  • Specific goals and requirements
  • Package deals and frequency

What You Get

🎯

Personalized Learning Plan

Tailored to your specific goals and current level

📊

Progress Tracking

Regular assessments and feedback on your improvement

🎓

Expert Instruction

Professional teacher with specialized certifications

🤝

Ongoing Support

Guidance and resources between lessons

{/* Final CTA Section */}

Ready to Join Our CELPIP Community?

Start with a free trial lesson and discover why our Speaking Club is the best way to improve your CELPIP score with other immigrants like you.

⏱️ 25 minutes
💰 Completely FREE
📝 No commitment
{/* Footer */}

Masha - English Teacher

Professional English instruction with a focus on results
